names.bio: Jadyn is a young English and French speaking actress who began acting at the young age of 4. She is known for her appearance in the Feature Film "Birthmarked" (2017) and "Arrival" (2016), and also for her role as Kaylee in the movie "Mommy's Little Boy" (2016). Jadyn has also appeared in the T.V. series Real Detective (2016). Jadyn can also be seen in a national commercial for LUVS diapers (2014) and a print ad for Rice Krispies (2015). When Jadyn is off screen, she enjoys singing and dancing, gymnastics, ice skating, and spending time with friends, family, and her cat and dog!
names.name: Jadyn Malone
